Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:03.19,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The girl is only one in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:05.09,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That made her the God of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:08.76,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,She found herself on an island when she began to understand things around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:10.75,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,There was nobody else around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:13.09,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,She had nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:15.95,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That was the everything the world offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.43,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.43,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Ouse," which means "Date."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.11,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.56,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.61,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,How far have you gotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't made much progress on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.78,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,About 30 percent of the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.03,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it alone after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.83,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,May I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:28.08,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"One day, the girl tried to light a fire on the beach."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:35.13,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Because there was an episode in a book about a person who lit a signal fire after being stranded on an island."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:39.01,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"A white line rose up to the deep, blue sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:43.72,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She thought, 'What's this thing that's just like a cloud?' and she put her face near it."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:46.10,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Her eyes and throat hurt badly."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:50.27,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She backed off in confusion and gazed at it from a distance."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.02,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She understood that it was useless."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:57.36,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Likewise, she began to understand one thing after another."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.74,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She understood what 'understanding' meant."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.62,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:04.91,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.91,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this girl is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Cute... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.21,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Should I rewrite it after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:14.54,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Which part?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.92,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Everything up till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.26,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:21.72,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Because you said she was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:25.68,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she should be described that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:30.18,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. A small episode like this is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.14,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:37.02,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This girl should be more abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Abnormal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:42.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Because the girl is taking things that seem to be a joke seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:46.45,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,the reader should get a sense of uneasiness and discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:51.33,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If she's thought to be cute, it means the girl isn't described properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.12,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Hoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.71,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,My, an obento?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.17,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-chan's share too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.67,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:07.85,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,As a housewife, it helps me that you're good at cooking, but as a mom, my feelings are more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:14.60,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Because if you're better than the girl you're dating, you won't be able to receive a love obento from her, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.61,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.61,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,You and Chihiro-chan aren't lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.74,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,We're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.74,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're so timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:29.79,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to be your lover after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.79,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's dangerous. That's dangerous, I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:35.29,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.79,0:04:35.29,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Fuan," which means "Anxiety."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:39.71,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:43.88,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nah. I was thinking about my career interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.51,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Career interests?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:48.68,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,A survey of what we want to do in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.14,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.77,MainF,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I received a career interest survey at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.60,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.03,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.65,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.16,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should just do what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:11.12,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be stressed if I knew what that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.20,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any idea at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.46,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any special talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.13,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Your cooking is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.13,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it some more thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.55,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 2,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.55,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Fuman," which means "Discontent."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.55,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.80,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.60,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.72,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,You're keeping it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.31,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You mean with the obento?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.81,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Or should I say with Chihiro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.27,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you could say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:43.73,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,It's helpful of you to save me the trouble of making breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.78,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two still aren't lovers yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:47.95,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,We're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:48.91,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.74,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:53.62,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that your response hadn't really changed somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:54.58,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:58.04,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Say, this is just "if."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:01.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,If Chihiro became my girlfriend, would you be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.13,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? If you're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:09.18,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Do you enjoy being with Chihiro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.39,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.60,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.10,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:22.98,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,You're a guy, so you should go out with her with a sense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.15,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.61,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Passion is like a downhill slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.03,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Once you take heart from it, it's unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.32,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,However, love is like an uphill slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:34.37,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,You have to carry the pains and difficulties while climbing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:42.00,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but the ones who go through difficulties are just couples, while the unstoppable ones are lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.25,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Love and passion are exact opposites.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:48.51,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,It's something like the inversion of the spelling of "Toufu" and "Nattou."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:48.51,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fscy150\move(352,-60,352,0,0,750)}A
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.13,0:06:48.51,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(352,-55,352,5,0,750)}TL Note: Toufu 【豆腐, bean curd】 literally means beans that have gone bad, while Nattou 【納豆, fermented soybeans】 literally means bad beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.01,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.43,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 2,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.43,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana there says "Giman," which means "Deception."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:07:00.85,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fscy100\move(352,0,352,-40,7500,8300)}A
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:07:00.85,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(,352,5,352,-35,7500,8300)}Most of the lines in this part of the story can be found in the opening animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:56.64,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She painted a human being."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:07:00.35,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She painted a boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:05.86,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"So, she decided to add a figure of a boy into paintings of landscapes she had painted."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:10.36,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She put up those paintings in the same places where she painted them."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.28,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"There was not a single place on the island she did not paint."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:17.91,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl was with the boy everywhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:21.58,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"It meant that the girl and the boy looked at each other every time she looked at the paintings."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.88,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"But the girl had no feeling of achievement."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:30.13,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Would it be a 'human'?" she thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:34.14,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"No. This was the 'painting of a human being.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:37.56,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"He did not move. He did not think. He was simply there."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.35,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Lonely?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:45.52,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Finally, she could ask herself by finding the word. She was not lonely."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.65,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.69,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:53.24,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you've made it to about 70 percent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.45,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Probably. Isn't it almost over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.29,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided on the ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.33,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.08,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.46,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,We've come up with two ideas so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:09.11,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,First, the girl enters the world of the paintings
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.59,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,and leaves behind the paintings of the boy and the girl living a peaceful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.01,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fantasy-type ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:17.72,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Second, the boy appears in her reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:22.10,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we haven't decided on the ending yet, it should be a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:28.02,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the first idea can turn into a happy ending or a sad ending, depending on your interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.61,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.82,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.61,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:38.91,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You can write the story of her entering the paintings as a fantasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:44.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can also think of it as her escaping from reality in order to run away from loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:50.92,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You can also think of the girl escaping from reality in order to run away from loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.34,MainF,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she breaks down?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.22,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she breaks down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.97,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It depends on the way you put it, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:02.98,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.89,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you've been worrying about this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:08.65,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I think she'll break down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:12.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The girl shouldn't know about loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.07,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:19.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But, if we decide to end the story like this, there's something I don't like about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.33,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:24.00,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it feel like God is playing with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.46,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I try, I can do it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.25,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:35.30,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Before I realized it, the story had already gotten much longer. It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.22,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.30,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:43.60,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I feel depressed that I wasn't able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.39,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:46.31,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:54.07,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:55.03,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.53,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.92,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:11.92,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah. You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.68,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.97,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:29.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun, do you want to... kiss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:33.19,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to kiss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You can go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.32,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I would say that to just anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:46.08,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,And it doesn't seem there was anyone else I've been this close to before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:53.96,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've continued to meet you till now because I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:59.09,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it seems you like me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:04.47,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can kiss me as a lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:09.98,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is the scene where we should kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.57,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.28,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I hesitating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:21.49,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I... Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:26.66,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If she's thought to be cute, it means the girl isn't described properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:30.12,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This girl should be more abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.25,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:35.59,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.88,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Something is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.68,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But how come Chihiro doesn't look happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.01,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,How come she's not shy about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.47,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,How come her expression doesn't change?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:54.40,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,How come she hasn't said a single word about liking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.48,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:01.65,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's because God is playing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.04,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.75,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:19.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.30,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.05,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.47,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:36.06,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't write down what happened just now in your diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.73,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't write it down... no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:46.20,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Everything... was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.83,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The girl is only one in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.87,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That made her the God of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.92,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.51,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:11.72,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I didn't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.36,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I wouldn't be able to get hold of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:27.36,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I gave up. But we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:33.41,MainT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's my whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:37.37,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I wonder if this is a bit too daring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:40.25,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It might be too stimulating for Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.26,Main,Miayko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.01,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.77,MainF,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(1000,3000,\1c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Papa. Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:00.61,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the preparations for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.03,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,This will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:19.04,MainT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,This is a place where sound has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:24.80,MainT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,One day, Mom vanished from Dad's heart, and Dad also vanished from Mom's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.89,MainF,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.47,MainF,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.23,MainF,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.37,bwT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,After that, sound vanished from this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.95,bwT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,After that, conversation vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:00.96,bwT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,All color vanished from my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:08.97,MainT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, even I vanished from their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.59,MainT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:15.22,bwT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I've been living in a world with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:37.70,MainT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,At last, I've found a world with sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.75,MainT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I've found a home with color.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:43.13,MainT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to shut myself in anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.76,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't answer your call right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:51.76,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please say your name and what I can do for you after the "beep."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:55.80,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! Hirono-kun, this is Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.56,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Have you woken up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:02.56,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to leave home. I'll get to our meeting place at noon, so don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.40,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Bye then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.32,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a heroic battle royal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.62,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,The rule of wild nature is harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:20.41,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:27.63,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! Hirono-kun, I'm already here. Are you on your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.92,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.56,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:41.23,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You should arrive ten minutes early when you go on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:44.44,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's a guy's obligation not to make the girl wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.52,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're late. You're late, late, late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.32,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to make me wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.74,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,As punishment, everything is your treat today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:55.99,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Hurry up and run here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:01.33,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Don't tell me you're sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.91,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If you overslept, I won't just let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:10.80,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-ro-no-kun! This is Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:14.55,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're still not coming? I'm waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.89,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.14,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,How many hours do you want me to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.73,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really planning on coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:37.99,MainT,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I will wipe you out from Onii-chan's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.45,MainT,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,He will then say farewell to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.41,MainT,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,And then, it will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.00,MainT,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I will end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.63,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to disappear again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:56.13,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:18:00.05,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Have you possibly mistaken our meeting place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:03.60,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's the bench in front of the fountain. You should know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:06.81,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If you're lost, call me. I'll come and pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.82,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,This is Miyako. Are you all right, Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.78,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have an accident on your way over, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.40,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Contact me right away after you hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:22.03,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this! At least contact me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.70,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You can at least give me a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.79,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:30.92,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,This is Miyako. Hirono-kun? Pick up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.42,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:35.71,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually listening to this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.47,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up the phone. Let's have a talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.18,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.06,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.72,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you pick up the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.35,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you answer my call?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.14,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.60,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you silent?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.40,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:55.03,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun? Please contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:58.36,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really mad or anything. I'll wait till we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.86,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep waiting till I hear your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.24,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I beg you......
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.25,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Come and see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.75,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:12.79,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:13.96,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Please......
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:19.34,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, you will come, right......?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:22.14,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I...... should keep waiting, right......?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:26.31,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you...... I believe you......
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:31.15,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Please...... answer me......
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:34.94,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You can answer me by mail too...... even a single word is fine......
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.57,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Please...... don't leave me alone......
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:41.07,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I will wait for you...... I will keep waiting for you......!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:46.33,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Why...... why......?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:51.29,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you promised me...... even though I believed you......
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.79,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Why.....?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.92,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Am I no good......?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.26,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Am I no good perhaps......?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.84,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me......?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:06.76,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, please tell me so......!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.64,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate me, just say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:13.69,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stay silent! Say something! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.27,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, please say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:23.07,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,...... I'm sorry...... I'm sorry that I said something weird......
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.74,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad......? You're mad, right......?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:34.79,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I always have things my own way...... say things as I like...... abuse you......
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:38.46,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...... I'm sorry......!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.80,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't manage to fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.72,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking forward to today's date.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:49.47,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought about you, my heart kept pounding......
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.64,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time having this feeling......
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:56.31,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what to do.......
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:21:01.19,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you...... I want to see you......
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:06.62,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Hirono-kun......
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.78,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Help me......!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:11.62,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear...... I don't want to disappear......!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:17.75,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear from your heart!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:57.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:23:00.85,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right. It's really not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:03.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the convenience store. Do you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:04.40,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Garibori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:05.90,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I meant dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:07.32,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Should I make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:08.61,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't frighten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:13.08,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean! I've been practicing my cooking recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:15.95,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me again when you don't need to practice anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:17.16,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can I just buy what I see fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:18.66,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:24.42,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What? Isn't it right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:34.81,Main,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,Deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:39.44,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Colorless colors are pure and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:44.57,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, ef - a tale of memories: Clear Color.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:47.94,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have memories you don't want to forget?
